New-patches: joachim.falk@gmx.de--2004-systemc-stuff/SystemC-VPC--mainline--0.1--patch-2
Summary: 
  -  change interface between Component and Scheduler
     now using the SchedulerProxy
     -> changing the Scheduler during simulation 
     schould be possible
  -  added a FCFS scheduler which uses this interface
  -  other Schedulers have to be changed to use the
     new interface

  -  also made a simple configuration file for mapping
  -  using an environment variable "VPCCONFIGURATION" to
     locate file
  -  Syntax is:
     component: HWM1 FCFS -> allokate a resource named "HWM1" 
                             using an "FCFS" Scheduler
     sim_mod.h_hca.qpc_manager HWM1 10 -> map "sim_mod.h_hca.qpc_manager"
                                          to "HWM1" using a
                                          delay of "10" ns
      - do not use comments!!!!!
      - and allokation before mapping!!!
      - uncomplete allokation or mapping maintains to
      broken assertions
     Simple example:
     ---
        component: HWM1 FCFS
        component: HWM2 FCFS
        component: HWM3 FCFS
        bla.foo1 HWM1 12
        bla.foo2 HWM2 111
        foobar HWM1 33
        ...
     ---
 
 -  another environment variable "VPCTRACEFILEPREFIX"
     is used as file name prefix of trace files
      - necessary while using two parallel simulator instances
